summary: What if Harry had long hair for the duration of his baby’s life so when he finally cuts it really short his baby starts to full...
question: What if Harry had long hair for the duration of his baby’s life so when he finally cuts it really short his baby starts to full on sob and starts pulling at his hair 😩
answer:
oh my gOD his baby angel’s mouth would just hang open and when it takes a collective second for the fact that his daddy, one he’s known for literally all of his eight months of tender living, with him having long curly hair, and has now his hair really short — he sobs. full-on sobs. throws a tantrum right then and there on his playmat. can’t even stop the tears rushing viciously down his chubby cheeks.

harry’s taken aback because although he did anticipate that baby angel might refuse his image for a couple seconds and only give him a funny look — he gets the maximum in that spectrum. he has him standing up, and it’s one of the times he’s stood up so strongly without any help, and marching over to him and pulling at his hair. with his mouth curling and eyes screwing and at this point it seemed like he wouldn’t stop that it’s gotten harry so concerned, trying to calm his baby back with all the ways he could think of in his time-pressured mind.

harry missed his hair too the moment his baby angel’s lips trembled.

:((

summary: Hi!! harry, fluff, 98, plus!size 🖤 hope you’re having a lovely day!
question: Hi!! harry, fluff, 98, plus!size 🖤 hope you’re having a lovely day!
answer:
Hope you are having a great day!!

If you don’t like it let me know and I will rewrite it for you! 

Let me know what you think

You and Harry were preparing to attend the Met gala, but this being the such an important fashion event you simply had to get the perfect outfit. Harry being close friends with the founder of Gucci really only had its perks, and getting a specially designed dress that was made for you and you only, there was not a thought of it going to anyone else, was definitely one of those perks.

You stood in the fitting room in nothing but your bra and panties, Harry sitting casually in the corner trying to hide just how lovely he thought you looked as you laughed with the seamstress, your tummy jiggling slightly with you chuckles, he loved you, all of you, every dimple and blemish, every scar and stretch mark, he loved all of you, even when you doubted it.

“Y/n, your dress has been altered, would you like to try it on,” Alessandro spoke, you turned to him nodding your head and back to Harry to make sure that he was up to date with everything that was going on, you looked at Harry and saw his eyes already on you, taking you in for all your worth, which to him was everything, he blew you a kiss as you walked out of the room. 

Stepping into the room your eyes landed on the most beautiful dress you had ever seen, and it was made for you. You walked forward and stood on the round ‘pedestal’ that was in the middle of the room as Alessandro grabbed your dress. Bringing it over to you, you raised your arms as the other designers grabbed your dress and slip it over your head, inhaling deeply you sucked in your tummy to squeeze the dress over it. But, once you let that breath go and your stomach returned to its beautifully natural state something popped, the seem of your dress busted slightly because of your tummy, and you couldn’t help but scream, and as soon as the sound of your panicked voice reached Harry’s ears he was running to the room, the door was locked as he tried to get in

“Baby, whats going on?” he asked through the wood

“Promise you won’t laugh?” you didn’t answer his question

“I promise baby,” he spoke with assurance and the door was opened for him, he saw that the dress had torn down the seem of your dress, he couldn’t help but let the laugh in his throat out

“I thought you said you wouldn’t laugh,” you spoke, your voice unstable due to your wavering confidence that you had just torn a dress

“Baby, I am not laughing at you, its a laugh of relief, I heard your scream and I thought you were in serious trouble, plus the dress will be fine, its along the seem, a quick fix, and even with it torn, my love you look stunning,”

Bringing it over to you, you raised your arms as the other designers grabbed your dress and slip it over your head, inhaling deeply you sucked in your tummy to squeeze the dress over it. But, once you let that breath go and your stomach returned to its beautifully natural state something popped, the seem of your dress busted slightly because of your tummy, and you couldn’t help but scream, and as soon as the sound of your panicked voice reached Harry’s ears he was running to the room, the door was locked as he tried to get in

“Baby, whats going on?” he asked through the wood

“Promise you won’t laugh?” you didn’t answer his question

“I promise baby,” he spoke with assurance and the door was opened for him, he saw that the dress had torn down the seem of your dress, he couldn’t help but let the laugh in his throat out

“I thought you said you wouldn’t laugh,” you spoke, your voice unstable due to your wavering confidence that you had just torn a dress

“Baby, I am not laughing at you, its a laugh of relief, I heard your scream and I thought you were in serious trouble, plus the dress will be fine, its along the seem, a quick fix, and even with it torn, my love you look stunning,”
